                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Preferences</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg">Personal style, comfort levels, and what makes you feel confident.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
                <div class="text-5xl font-black number-badge mb-4">04</div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Availability</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg">What clothes are clean and accessible in your closet right now?</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-700 to-teal-800 text-white rounded-2xl p-12 diagonal-section">
            <div class="max-w-3xl">
                <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 opacity-80">Key Insight</p>
                <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold leading-snug">
                    While weather apps and closet apps exist separately, no solution combines wardrobe, weather, and calendar in a single glanceable interface.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Competitive Analysis -->
    <div class="mb-32 scroll-reveal">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 mb-12">
            <div class="md:col-span-1">
                <h2 class="text-5xl font-black mb-6 leading-tight">Competitive<br/>Analysis</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-2">
