                    My teammate Shelby had designed the mobile app using a horizontal scrolling card layout. After reviewing her work, I realized this approach was:
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-700">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
